Another for sickness of pregnancy when there is pain. Take laurel berries and make fine powder and give the patient a spoonful in warm red wine in the evening or the morning, according to the hour when the pain assaults her. When she takes it, she should stay in repose. Do this once or twice or more, according to when you find that it works, and soon you will cure her.

Make a fomentation under the nose with an old shoe and soon you will cure the sickness of pregnancy.

